otrack can be well detected. Our\nresults would be useful for the development of novel spintronic devices based\non moveable spin textures.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 9 Aug 2016 18:50:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 16 Feb 2017 16:17:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-03-09"}
