ons of the\nmodel. The pair correlation function $g (r; t)$ for $w = 1/8$ has a well\ndefined oscillatory structure at $10t_M$, with a minimum at $r\\approx\\mu$ and\nmaximum at $r \\approx 1.5\\mu$, but this structure is not observed for $w \\ge\n1/4$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 9 Aug 2016 19:32:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-10-03"}
