 excesses in M31 and M33; future studies should be aimed at better\nconstraining theoretical predictions to compliment existing and future\nobservational data.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 9 Aug 2016 20:00:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-17"}
