tedly, the soft intra-monomer\noscillations pertain to distortions that do not create inter-monomer steric\nclashes in the assembly, suggesting that structural optimization of the\nassembly evolved at all levels of complexity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 9 Aug 2016 20:15:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 5 Nov 2016 22:06:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-08"}
