able to\nthat in the Class II phase because large gas surface density is expected and\nlarge amount of dust is supplied by envelope-to-disk accretion.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 Aug 2016 00:50:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 14 Feb 2017 02:35:25 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 15 Jun 2017 01:10:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-06-16"}
