 or one associated\njet is reported. The measurements are compared to theoretical predictions and\nfound in good agreement.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 Aug 2016 08:50:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 7 Nov 2016 16:05:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-08"}
