ilon)$ forests when $a=\\Omega(\\log\nn)$ and into $a (1+\\epsilon)$ pseduo-forests when $a=o(\\log n)$. Obtaining an\nefficient distributed decomposition into less than $2a$ forests was stated as\nthe 10th open problem in the book by Barenboim and Elkin.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 Aug 2016 15:53:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-11"}
